nson andamp; Johnson, New Brunswick, N.J.   S.C. Johnson andamp; Sons, Racine, Wis.   Lancaster Laboratories, Lancaster, Pa.   Lincoln National Corp., Fort Wayne, Ind.   Little Tikes, Hudson, Ohio.   Lost Arrow, Ventura, Calif.   Lourdes Hospital, Binghamton, N.Y.   MNC Financial, Baltimore.   Marriott, Washington.   Catherine McAuley Health System, Ann Arbor, Mich.   Merck andamp; Co., Rahway, N.J.   3M, St. Paul, Minn.   Morrison andamp; Foerster, San Francisco.   NCNB, Charlotte, N.C.   Official Airline Guides, Oak Brook, Ill.   Oracle, Redwood Shores, Calif.   Phoenix Mutual Life Insurance, Hartford, Conn.   Pitney Bowes, Stamford, Conn.   Procter andamp; Gamble, Cincinnati, Ohio.   SAS Institute, Cary, N.C.   South Shore Bank, Chicago.   Steelcase, Grand Rapids, Mich.   Stride Rite, Cambridge, Mass.   Syntex, Palo Alto, Calif.   Tenneco, Houston.   Trammell Crow Co., Dallas.   The Travelers Corp., Hartford, Conn.   United States Hosiery Corporation, Lincolnton, N.C.   Unum, Portland, Maine.   U.S. West, Englewood, Colo.   Warner-Lambert, Morris Plains, N.J.   Wegmans, Rochester, N.Y.   Wells Fargo andamp; Co., San Francisco.   Xerox, Stamford, Conn.</TEXT></DOC>